    IC Funded uses a performance-based scaling model that lets traders grow their capital over time, up to a maximum total allocation of <strong>$500,000</strong> (hence why scaling isn't available for this account size). Scaling is not automatic and doesn't follow a fixed step-up schedule &mdash; eligibility is based on consistent profitability, strict rule compliance, and successful payouts on a funded account.
